      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·010.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">文王有聲.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>文王有聲，遹駿有聲。遹求厥寧，遹觀厥成。文王烝哉。
文王受命，有此武功。既伐于崇，作邑于豐。文王烝哉。
築城伊淢，作豐伊匹。匪棘其欲，遹追來孝。王后烝哉。
王公伊濯，維豐之垣。四方攸同，王后維翰。王后烝哉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>King Wăn is famous;
Yea, he is very famous.
What he sought was the repose (of the people);
What he saw was the completion (of his work).
A sovereign true was king Wăn!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-wenwang-010__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
